params.user_prompt:
Write a story that tells an image of myself as a future self based on this description:  
target_or_desire:  {{workflow.parameters.target_or_desire}},  
things_to_have: {{workflow.parameters.things_to_have}},  
how_to_be_someone: {{workflow.parameters.how_to_be_someone}},  
how_life_should_look: {{workflow.parameters.how_life_should_look}}
